  "budget_request": "Annotated Budget Request to the Victoria State Government: CFA Rapid Bushfire Response requests AUD 153400.0 for an initial drone division. The request purchases 11 SSA drones and 2 radio-repeater drones at the official AUD 10000 unit cost, plus a training and spares reserve. The mix balances surveillance, communications, topography, event size, event frequency, firefighter safety, and economics. A decade projection is included because increasing extreme fire likelihood can require extra equipment even when drone unit cost stays constant.",
